## 🔢 Urutan Implementasi (MVP Priority)

1. **Config Filters** — register filter agar route group bekerja
2. **Shared Layout** — template sidebar reusable
3. **Super Admin: Leads CRM** — CRUD + followup + pipeline
4. **Super Admin: Paket Langganan** — CRUD
5. **Super Admin: Restoran** — CRUD + konversi lead
6. **RestaurantAdmin: Profile** — edit profil resto
7. **RestaurantAdmin: Kategori** — CRUD
8. **RestaurantAdmin: Menu** — CRUD + upload gambar
9. **RestaurantAdmin: Meja** — CRUD + generate QR
10. **Customer: Scan QR** — identifikasi meja & restoran
11. **Customer: Menu** — tampilkan menu + keranjang
12. **Customer: Checkout** — form + pilih bayar
13. **Kitchen Display** — lihat & update status pesanan
14. **Cashier: Konfirmasi** — bayar cash/QRIS
15. **RestaurantAdmin: Dashboard** — statistik real
16. **RestaurantAdmin: Laporan** — harian & bulanan
17. **CRM Pelanggan otomatis** — update saat order selesai
